VPC flow captures data at the interface level as well as the VPC level.
we can ship the logs to s3 bucket/cloud-watch logs.


Flow logs do not capture all the IP traffic some of them includes::
- Traffic generted by instnace when they contact amazon DNS server
- traffic generated by windows licence activitaton
- DHCP traffic
- traffic to and from 169.254.169.254 instance meta data
